					<h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">口红填充机</h2>				</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-47c97269 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider" data-id="47c97269" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="divider.default">
							<div class="elementor-divider">
			<span class="elementor-divider-separator">
						</span>
		</div>
						</div>
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5fb0d5c3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="5fb0d5c3" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
									<p>口红灌装机是一种用于将口红、唇膏及唇彩定量灌装至管体、模具或容器中的容积式计量设备。可采用半自动或全自动系统设计。根据用户需求说明（URS），Npack可为客户量身定制以上两种类型的口红灌装机。</p><p>为满足现代化妆品生产多样化的需求，市面上现有多种类型的口红灌装机——每种均针对特定产品形态及产量规模定制设计。Npack采用的先进潜入式灌装头在填充模具时，可根据灌装容量速度精确控制其上升速度，实现精准灌装。</p>								</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-53d6746e e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child" data-id="53d6746e" data-element_type="container" data-e-type="container">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-21ef27b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-video" data-id="21ef27b5" data-element_type="widget" data-e-type="widget" data-settings="{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/youtu.be\/rE8V0oCNxp8&quot;,&quot;show_image_overlay&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;image_overlay&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.npackpm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/12\/2025122002422799.webp&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:5113,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;alt&quot;:&quot;how to filling lipstick?&quot;,&quot;source&quot;:&quot;library&quot;},&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}" data-widget_type="video.default">
